            "text_Upz3Mm": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We source fabrics with uncompromising attention to detail, starting with the yarn — compact or fine — as it sets the foundation. Colors are carefully selected, often guided by Pantones, and dyed through precise processes to achieve the perfect texture, finish, and hand-feel. </p><p>Our fabrics must deliver softness, breathability, and stretch, while maintaining their shape, color, and quality through countless wears. Whether built for streetwear performance or casual luxury, each fabric reflects our brand’s identity.</p>",
