    "testimonial_TkXRJ8": {
      "type": "Testimonial",
      "blocks": {
        "add_hNripH": {
          "type": "add",
          "settings": {
            "cs_product": "club-house-jersey-top",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_20.png",
            "rich-text": "<p>I am absolutely obsessed with the half-zip I ordered! The quality of the fabric is incredible—it's super comfortable but holds its shape perfectly. It fits exactly how I wanted it to, with that perfect relaxed streetwear look. 'Our Terms' definitely nailed it. I’ve already gotten so many compliments!</p>",
            "name": "Alex M.",
            "icon-text": "@rayan"
          }
        },
        "add_qnb8w7": {
          "type": "add",
          "settings": {
            "cs_product": "cropped-zipper-hoodie-for-women",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_21.png",
            "rich-text": "<p>Honestly one of the best online shopping experiences I've had in a while. The shipping was fast, and the apparel looks even better in person than it does on the site. You can tell they put a lot of thought into the design and materials. </p>",
            "name": "Alex M.",
            "icon-text": "@rayan"
          }
        },
        "add_KUkJ4a": {
          "type": "add",
          "settings": {
            "cs_product": "pink-hue-t-shirt-for-men",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_22.png",
            "rich-text": "<p>Finally, a brand that gets it right. The 'Our Terms' gear is stylish, effortless, and feels incredibly premium. It’s rare to find pieces that are this comfortable while still looking put-together. </p>",
            "name": "Alex M.",
            "icon-text": "@rayan"
          }
        },
        "add_8Hiz9a": {
          "type": "add",
          "settings": {
            "cs_product": "terms-print-tee-for-women",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_23.png",
            "rich-text": "<p>This has quickly become the most worn item in my closet. The 'Our Terms' half-zip is so versatile—I throw it on for running errands, heading to the gym, or just hanging out, and it always looks good.</p>",
            "name": "Alex M.",
            "icon-text": "@rayan"
          }
        },
        "add_GBF98M": {
          "type": "add",
          "settings": {
            "cs_product": "terms-print-tee-for-women",
