            "rich-text": "<p>This has quickly become the most worn item in my closet. The 'Our Terms' half-zip is so versatile—I throw it on for running errands, heading to the gym, or just hanging out, and it always looks good.</p>",
            "name": "Alex M.",
            "icon-text": "@rayan"
          }
        }
      },
